  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405580/extras/e1e74dc1fa9678dc598fbec18becb63b.poster.avif?t=1737039251\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405580/extras/e1e74dc1fa9678dc598fbec18becb63b.webm?t=1737039251\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405580/extras/e1e74dc1fa9678dc598fbec18becb63b.mp4?t=1737039251\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Chosen by the Moon, Save the Ruined World</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>In a desolate world, mysterious dungeons have emerged. Blessed with the power to resurrect through lunar energy, you must survive in this world of chaos.</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Endless Growth, Powerful Enemies and Bosses</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The protagonist 'Moon Shard' possesses the ability to resurrect with all acquired powers intact through lunar energy.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>For newcomers, this dungeon may prove extremely challenging.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fear not - by defeating enemies, you'll earn experience and MoonLight Points to purchase growth-enhancing items from the Witch's Shop.</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Can You Conquer the Ever-changing Dungeon Structure?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Uniquely, the dungeon's layout transforms with each entry.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405580/extras/f306420b04a99e5d668d790e824f68c1.avif?t=1737039251\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405580/extras_big/f306420b04a99e5d668d790e824f68c1.avif?t=1737039251 width=800 height=260 /></span></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>But fear not - somewhere in the dungeon lies the boss's gatekeeper. While weaker than the boss, they are much stronger than other enemies.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Can you conquer the dungeon even with endless growth?</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Card System</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405580/extras/c14d6489e7710e2208cdebed4c35304c.avif?t=1737039251\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405580/extras_big/c14d6489e7710e2208cdebed4c35304c.avif?t=1737039251 width=800 height=450 /></span></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>                                 Common / Rare / Epic / Legendary tiers available,</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Epic and Legendary cards are extremely rare to find, but the moment you level up and see these tiers, you'll be filled with pure excitement.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Make your best judgment to select the finest cards, defeat the boss, and clear the dungeon!</strong></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405580/extras/e1e74dc1fa9678dc598fbec18becb63b.poster.avif?t=1737039251\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405580/extras/e1e74dc1fa9678dc598fbec18becb63b.webm?t=1737039251\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405580/extras/e1e74dc1fa9678dc598fbec18becb63b.mp4?t=1737039251\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Chosen by the Moon, Save the Ruined World</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>In a desolate world, mysterious dungeons have emerged. Blessed with the power to resurrect through lunar energy, you must survive in this world of chaos.</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Endless Growth, Powerful Enemies and Bosses</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The protagonist 'Moon Shard' possesses the ability to resurrect with all acquired powers intact through lunar energy.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>For newcomers, this dungeon may prove extremely challenging.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fear not - by defeating enemies, you'll earn experience and MoonLight Points to purchase growth-enhancing items from the Witch's Shop.</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Can You Conquer the Ever-changing Dungeon Structure?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Uniquely, the dungeon's layout transforms with each entry.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405580/extras/f306420b04a99e5d668d790e824f68c1.avif?t=1737039251\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405580/extras_big/f306420b04a99e5d668d790e824f68c1.avif?t=1737039251 width=800 height=260 /></span></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>But fear not - somewhere in the dungeon lies the boss's gatekeeper. While weaker than the boss, they are much stronger than other enemies.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Can you conquer the dungeon even with endless growth?</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Card System</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405580/extras/c14d6489e7710e2208cdebed4c35304c.avif?t=1737039251\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405580/extras_big/c14d6489e7710e2208cdebed4c35304c.avif?t=1737039251 width=800 height=450 /></span></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>                                 Common / Rare / Epic / Legendary tiers available,</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Epic and Legendary cards are extremely rare to find, but the moment you level up and see these tiers, you'll be filled with pure excitement.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Make your best judgment to select the finest cards, defeat the boss, and clear the dungeon!</strong></p>",
